# Social Card Images

Create the following images for social sharing:

## og-image.png
- Size: 1200x630px
- Format: PNG or JPG
- Used by: Facebook, LinkedIn, other Open Graph platforms
- Design tips:
  - Feature your logo/brand
  - Show main value proposition: "Minifi - Free URL Shortener"
  - Include URL: https://minifi-url.vercel.app
  - Use high contrast colors
  - Avoid text near edges (safe zone: 40px)

## twitter-card.png
- Size: 1200x628px (or 1200x675px for larger cards)
- Format: PNG or JPG
- Used by: Twitter/X
- Design tips:
  - Similar to og-image but optimized for Twitter
  - Can be the same as og-image in most cases

## Current placeholders needed:
- /public/og-image.png (1200x630px)
- /public/twitter-card.png (1200x628px)

Referenced in meta tags as:
- https://minifi-url.vercel.app/og-image.png
- https://minifi-url.vercel.app/twitter-card.png

Use tools like:
- Canva (canva.com)
- Figma (figma.com)
- OG Image Generator (og-playground.vercel.app)
